summary: This is an email chain from June 15, 2021, between FBI personnel and a victim specialist, scheduling a meeting to discuss the Maxwell trial and discovery matters. It indicates ongoing coordination within the prosecution team.

events.title: Scheduled Meeting on Maxwell Trial/Discovery
events.description: A meeting is scheduled for Thursday (June 17, 2021) between 1:00-1:30 PM to discuss the Maxwell trial and discovery matters.

keyFacts: The document is an email chain dated June 15, 2021, concerning the scheduling of a meeting about the Maxwell trial and discovery.
Participants include FBI personnel and a victim specialist from the New York office, indicating coordination within the prosecution team.
The meeting was scheduled for Thursday, June 17, 2021, between 1:00 PM and 1:30 PM.
